&lt;li&gt;Org Stabilization: Guide newly formed teams through the stabilization phase: establish team norms, resolve early friction, and ensure leaders are set up for sustainable success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Border Alignment: Serve as the connective tissue between U.S. Tech/AI teams and HQ, driving alignment on people strategy, headcount planning, and organizational change.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
